{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-033","title":"Sentence 33","sectionId":"sentences-031","sectionTitle":"Sentence 31-40","pageStart":228,"pageEnd":232,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":21,"duplicateEntryCount":5,"pages":[{"number":228,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 33"},{"type":"text","text":"With no oceans to dissolve it, outgassed carbon dioxide began to"},{"type":"text","text":"accumulate in the atmosphere, intensifying the greenhouse effect even"},{"type":"text","text":"more."},{"type":"text","text":"没有海洋溶解二氧化碳，排出的二氧化碳开始在大气中聚集，"},{"type":"text","text":"进一步加剧了温室效应。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句主干是Carbon dioxide began to accumulate in the atmosphere。"},{"type":"text","text":"句首是with引导的独立主格结构。句尾的intensifying the greenhouse"},{"type":"text","text":"effect even more是现在分词短语作结果状语。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"outgas /ˌaʊtˈɡæs/ v. 除去（固体中的）气；放气","headword":"outgas"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 out（出来）+gas（气体）→让气体出来→放气"},{"type":"entry","text":"carbon /ˈkɑːrbən/ n. 碳","headword":"carbon"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 carbon emission碳排放"},{"type":"entry","text":"dioxide /daɪˈɑːksaɪd/ n. 二氧化物","headword":"dioxide"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 di（二）+ox（氧）+ide→二氧化物"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 sulphur dioxide 二氧化硫"},{"type":"entry","text":"accumulate /əˈkjuːmjəleɪt/ v. 积累；积聚；","headword":"accumulate"},{"type":"text","text":"（数量）逐渐增加"}]},{"number":229,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ac（表加强）+cumul（堆积）+ate→堆积"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 amass vt. 积累，积聚"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 accumulation n. 积聚"},{"type":"entry","text":"intensify /ɪnˈtensɪfaɪ/ v. 加强；增强；加剧","headword":"intensify"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 heighten v. 提高；增强"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 intensification n. 增强；强化"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“全球变暖”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"anthropogenic /ˌænθrəpəʊˈdʒɛnɪk/ a. 人为的","headword":"anthropogenic"},{"type":"note","text":"搭